                <h2 id="impact">8. Impact of Disabling Cookies</h2>

                <h3>Disabling Essential Cookies</h3>
                <p>
                    Blocking essential cookies will significantly impact your experience on Clear Window:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Cannot log in:</strong> Authentication requires session cookies</li>
                    <li><strong>Cannot submit reviews:</strong> Security tokens are needed to prevent fraud</li>
                    <li><strong>Lost preferences:</strong> Your settings won't be saved between visits</li>
                    <li><strong>Reduced security:</strong> Protection against certain attacks may not function</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Disabling Functional Cookies</h3>
                <p>If you disable functional cookies:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Your theme preference (dark/light mode) won't be remembered</li>
                    <li>Language settings will reset to default</li>
                    <li>You'll need to reconfigure accessibility settings on each visit</li>
                    <li>Some enhanced features may not work properly</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Disabling Analytics Cookies</h3>
                <p>Disabling analytics cookies has minimal impact on functionality:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>All core features continue to work normally</li>
                    <li>Your usage won't contribute to our improvement efforts</li>
                    <li>We won't be able to understand how users interact with new features</li>
                </ul>

